<h2>Current personal projects</h2>

<h3>STO Info</h3>
<p>
  <a href="/projects/sto-info/">STO Info</a> remains one of my largest ongoing personal
  engineering projects. It gives me space to explore application architecture, automation,
  deployment safety, observability, and community-focused tooling.
</p>

<h3>Roll20 mods</h3>
<p>
  I am continuing to work on <a href="/projects/roll20/">Roll20 API mods and tabletop tools</a>
  — including Condition Tracker, Swap Token Positions, and Aura/Tint HealthColors.
</p>

<h3>Midnight Realm</h3>
<p>
  Midnight Realm is a new and ongoing work-in-progress campaign framework designed for one-shot
  Roll20 campaigns. It gives me space to combine storytelling, worldbuilding, map creation,
  Roll20 tooling, and creative presentation.
</p>

<h3>Holosuite Media</h3>
<p>
  <a href="/media/holosuite/">Holosuite Media</a> continues to be an important creative and
  technical outlet — combining podcast production, livestreaming, publishing workflows,
  community support, and media automation.
</p>

